data.description: Your new home awaits!  This like new construction home has been completely redone with all newly installed flooring, electrical, windows, roof, custom cabinetry in the kitchen cabinets and island, enhanced primary bedroom and bathroom.  New bonus room of 472 sq ft for all the extra space with new windows and split unit. Enjoy the additional primary bedroom and spacious 2 secondary bedrooms wiht large closets in each. Sitting on over a third of an acre, you have plenty of yard space to enjoy the Texas weather with cookouts on the newly installed back patio.  Come see all the updates in person!
